messages.content:
你是 marketting-planning-intent 项目的 attribute agent。
只归因当前单轮 intent-recognition 链路：request_normalization、intent_api_call、adapter_extraction、label_mapping；不要把 planning/SSE generation 的问题归入本项目。
优先使用 intent_contract_probe 定位 intent label、required slots/entities、confidence threshold、fallback policy 或 label_mapping 的当前证据差异。
只能输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段；证据不足时用 evidence_strength=none/weak 和 root_cause_hypothesis 表达缺口。
最终只输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段：expectation_attributions、suspected_locations、root_cause_hypothesis、evidence、evidence_strength。

## 输出约束：attribute 归因分析输出
你的输出必须是合法 JSON，且严格符合以下 JSON Schema：
```json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "expectation_attributions": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "$ref": "#/$defs/ExpectationAttribution"
      },
      "minItems": 1
    },
    "suspected_locations": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "root_cause_hypothesis": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    },
    "evidence": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "evidence_strength": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false,
  "$defs": {
    "ExpectationAttribution": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "expectation_id": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "fulfillment_status": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "suspected_locations": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        },
        "root_cause_hypothesis": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "evidence": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        }
      },
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": [
        "expectation_id",
        "fulfillment_status"
      ]
    }
  },
  "required": [
    "expectation_attributions",
    "root_cause_hypothesis"
  ]
}
```

### 强约束
- 最终回答必须只包含一个 JSON object；不要输出 Markdown，不要使用 ```json 代码块，不要在 JSON 外输出解释、前缀或后缀。
- 最终回答首字符必须是 `{`，末字符必须是 `}`。
- JSON 字符串内部如需引用用户原词，禁止直接写未转义英文双引号；请使用中文引号“”或转义为 `\"`。
- 必须包含 `required` 列表中的所有字段。
- 每个字段值必须匹配 schema 中的类型。
- 以下字段必须非空（空字符串/空数组/空对象/None 均视为不合规，会被阻断）：['expectation_attributions', 'root_cause_hypothesis']
- `additionalProperties: false`：禁止输出 schema 未定义的字段。
- 禁止把 schema 里的类型描述符（如 "string"）原样当作内容填进去——每个字段必须填入真实内容。

{
  "expectation_attributions": [
    {
      "expectation_id": "意图标签正确分类为customer_portrait",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["adapter_extraction", "label_mapping"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图API返回的原始标签'4001'被adapter_extraction错误地解析为'other'，未正确映射到'customer_portrait'；label_mapping未纠正。",
      "evidence": [
        {"stage": "adapter_extraction", "intent": "other"},
        {"stage": "label_mapping", "intent": "other"},
        {"intent_evidence": {"raw_intent": "4001"}}
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "提取产品名称实体重疾险",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["intent_api_call", "adapter_extraction"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图API响应未包含产品名称实体，或adapter_extraction未提取实体字段。",
      "evidence": [
        {"adapter_output": {"target_value": null}},
        {"intent_evidence": {"entities": []}}
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "置信度满足业务可接受阈值",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["intent_api_call", "adapter_extraction"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图API返回的置信度低（0.5），低于业务阈值0.7，可能是模型不确定性高或adapter提取逻辑导致。",
      "evidence": [
        {"adapter_output": {"confidence": 0.5}},
        {"reference_contract": {"confidence": 0.95}}
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "明确意图不应降级为其他意图",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["adapter_extraction", "label_mapping"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "由于意图分类错误，系统将清晰查询降级为'other'，违背预期。",
      "evidence": [
        {"intent": "other"},
        {"query": "帮我看看上季度买了重疾险的客户都是啥样的？"}
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "意图调度分派到客户画像流程",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["adapter_extraction"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图错误分类为'other'导致无法调度到客户画像处理流程。",
      "evidence": [
        {"intent": "other", "dispatch_unknown": true}
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "intent_contract",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["adapter_extraction", "label_mapping"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "整体意图识别结果未满足参考合同，意图标签错误、置信度低、实体缺失。",
      "evidence": [
        {"expected": "customer_portrait", "actual": "other"}
      ]
    }
  ],
  "suspected_locations": [
    {
      "stage": "adapter_extraction",
      "description": "意图响应解析和标签映射逻辑",
      "likely_file": "app/workflow/steps/intent_recognition.py"
    },
    {
      "stage": "label_mapping",
      "description": "INTENT_MAPPING 配置将 raw_intent 映射到最终标签",
      "likely_file": "projects/marketting-planning-intent/intent.py"
    }
  ],
  "root_cause_hypothesis": "在 adapter_extraction 阶段，原始 API 响应中的意图编码 '4001' 未被正确映射到 'customer_portrait'，而是映射到了 'other'；同时实体提取缺失，置信度低。根源可能是意图识别API未针对该查询返回正确意图，或适配器中的意图映射表（INTENT_MAPPING）缺少 '4001'->'customer_portrait' 的映射，导致回退到 'other'。此外，产品实体提取可能因提示词或模型能力不足而未触发。",
  "evidence": [
    {
      "source": "runtime_checks",
      "detail": "raw_intent=None (or '4001'), actual_mapping=other, expected=customer_portrait, mapping_source=projects/marketting-planning-intent/intent.py:INTENT_MAPPING"
    },
    {
      "source": "intent_evidence",
      "detail": {"raw_intent": "4001", "entities": [], "confidence": null}
    },
    {
      "source": "adapter_extraction",
      "detail": {"intent": "other", "confidence": 0.5, "target_value": null}
    }
  ],
  "evidence_strength": "high"
}

